## Sample Fidelity Checklist

**Bedtime Routine**

| Step | Task | Completed | Notes |
|:---:|------|:---:|-------|
| 1 | Gave 10-minute advance warning | ☐ Yes  ☐ No | |
| 2 | Gave 5-minute advance warning | ☐ Yes  ☐ No | |
| 3 | Started timer for bedtime routine | ☐ Yes  ☐ No | |
| 4 | Followed visual schedule for routine steps | ☐ Yes  ☐ No | |
| 5 | Offered limited choices during routine | ☐ Yes  ☐ No | |
| 6 | Incorporated brief preferred activity | ☐ Yes  ☐ No | |
</Markdown>

<Markdown id="fba3_checklist_escape_response">
## Response to Escape Behavior

| Step | Task | Completed | Notes |
|:---:|------|:---:|-------|
| 7 | Ignored escape behaviors (did not chase) | ☐ Yes  ☐ No | |
| 8 | Did not negotiate or argue | ☐ Yes  ☐ No | |
| 9 | Provided sticker/praise for compliance | ☐ Yes  ☐ No | |
| 10 | Honored bedtime pass if used | ☐ Yes  ☐ No | |
</Markdown>
