<Vertical id="fba3_reflection">
<Markdown>
## Final Reflection

You have determined that the modified intervention was a success! Write a brief reflection of the experience, addressing the following points:

1. Whether the behavior was successfully or unsuccessfully modified
2. What aspects of the intervention were effective and not effective
3. Whether your plan was too complicated, simple, or just right
4. Your personal reflections about the execution of this project, including what could have been done differently — provide at least 2 specific examples of what changes you would have made if Annie's roommate were to continue to babysit Johnny
</Markdown>

<TextArea id="fba3_reflection_text" rows="10" placeholder="Write your reflection here..." />
